ğŸš€ How to Execute Tests

ğŸ›  Prerequisites
- Java 21 installed
- Maven installed
- Chrome browser (or update config for other browsers)

â–¶ï¸ Run Tests
`bash
mvn clean test
`

ğŸ“Š View Reports
- Cucumber HTML: target/cucumber-reports.html
- Extent Report: reports/ExtentReport.html
- Screenshots: screenshots/
- Logs: logs/
